  @{u}PacMan'96 SCREENMODE:@{uu}

   By selecting this menu entry you can free select
   the screenmode PacMan'96 is running at.

   By pressing the left/right cursor keys or by draging
   the joystick left/right you can switch between 
   <SCREENMODE> and <WINDOW ON WB>.

   If you press the RETURN key or the fire button on 
   your joystick your choice is confirmed.

   <SCREENMODE>
    An standard requester apears on the Workbench
    where you can select the wanted screenmode.

   <WINDOW ON WB>
