@Toc MainOptions
@Prev OptLoadLev
@Next OptReturn

  @{u}PacMan'96 SAVE OPTIONS:@{uu}

   By selecting this entry all settings can be written
   to disk.

   A file called "PacMan.Options" is written to the 
   PacMan'96 directory which contains these settings:

    * Control options for both players (JOYSTICK/KEYBOARD)
    * Taskpriority
    * Screen mode
    * Window mode 
    * Windowposition on the Workbench
    * Musicsettings
    * Music/Soundeffect Volume of all tracks
@EndNode



